<emphasis id="B90BAA39FFDE3365FC1A594DFC18D359" box="[906,966,289,313]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="276">ampli</emphasis>
= wider, 
<emphasis id="B90BAA39FFDE3365FBBC594EFBB1D359" box="[1068,1135,290,313]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="276">cornis</emphasis>
= anntenae in Latin.
</paragraph>
